Project Architecture
Tech Stack
Backend: Spring Boot, Spring Security, Spring Data JPA
Database: MySQL (or H2 for simplicity)
Build Tool: Maven
Testing: Postman
Modules and Layers
Controller Layer:
Handles incoming HTTP requests and sends responses.
Service Layer:
Business logic.
Repository Layer:
Database interactions using Spring Data JPA.
Database Schema
Tables:
users: Stores user details.
products: Stores product catalog.
carts: Stores user-specific cart data.
orders: Stores order details.
order_items: Stores order item details.
